            </div>
        </li>#}
    </ul>    
</div>
<div id="news" class="fl half-width right">
    <h2>Latest news</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <span class="note">12/08/2012</span>
            <p>We&rsquo;re continuing to work on exciting new noodleDig features. Keep watching this space for updates. In the coming months we&rsquo;ll be adding music to noodleDig, as well as giving you more chance to comment on other people&rsquo;s stuff! Cool, eh?</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="note">05/08/2012</span>
            <p>We&rsquo;re working to make noodleDig faster and more responsive to all your noodly needs. Please continue to bear with us.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="note">30/07/2012</span>
            <p>Just working on making our YouTube search a bit more accurate and we&rsquo;re going to give you a way to suggest your own searches (within reason).</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

